# NomadSpace Design System (Figma → SwiftUI)

## Design Tokens

### Colors
| Token | HEX | RGB | SwiftUI |
|-------|-----|-----|---------|
| accent | #2196F3 | 33, 150, 243 | NomadColors.accent |
| highlight | #FF9500 | 255, 149, 0 | NomadColors.highlight |
| surface | #F2F3F5 | 242, 243, 245 | NomadColors.surface |
| onSurface | #212121 | 33, 33, 33 | NomadColors.onSurface |
| onSurfaceSecondary | #878787 | 135, 135, 135 | NomadColors.onSurfaceSecondary |
| success | #34C759 | 52, 199, 89 | NomadColors.success |
| error | #F04438 | 240, 68, 56 | NomadColors.error |
| cardBackground | #FFFFFF | 255, 255, 255 | NomadColors.cardBackground |

### Typography
| Style | Size | Weight | SwiftUI |
|-------|------|--------|---------|
| largeTitle | 28pt | Bold, Rounded | NomadFonts.largeTitle |
| title | 22pt | Semibold, Rounded | NomadFonts.title |
| headline | 17pt | Semibold | NomadFonts.headline |
| body | 15pt | Regular | NomadFonts.body |
| caption | 13pt | Regular | NomadFonts.caption |
| small | 11pt | Regular | NomadFonts.small |

### Spacing
- Card padding: 16pt
- Section spacing: 20pt
- Corner radius: 12pt (buttons), 16pt (cards)
- Shadow: 0 2 8, opacity 0.06

## Components
- **NomadCard**: 16pt padding, 16pt radius, white bg, subtle shadow
- **NomadButton**: primary (accent fill), secondary (accent 10% fill), outline (border only)
- **NomadTextField**: icon + text field with caption

